data.enText: no longer doing sth or dealing with sb/sth

data.chText: 我还得一小时以后才能完成。
data.enText: I won't be finished for another hour.

data.chText: 你我之间的交道还没有完。
data.enText: I'm not finished with you yet.
no longer powerful, effective or able to continue

data.chText: 如果报界发现这些问题，他的政治生涯就完了。
data.enText: If the newspapers find out, he's finished in politics.
fully completed, especially in a particular way

means: 吃完，喝光，用尽(所剩之物)

example: after the revolution the aristocracy was finished
the unsuccessful run for office left him ruined politically and economically

tr: ended or brought to an end
(of materials or goods) brought to the desired final state
having a surface coating or finish applied
example: the finished bookcase costs much more than the unfinished ones

tr: (of skills or the products of skills) brought to or having the greatest excellence
example: a dazzling and finished piece of writing

value.def: Someone who is finished with something is no longer doing it or dealing with it or is no longer interested in it.

example.ex: One suspects he will be finished with boxing.
example.tran: 人们猜想他不会再打拳了。

value.tran: 不再做(…)的;(同…)不再打交道的;(对…)不再感兴趣的

value.def: Something that is finished no longer exists or is no longer happening.

example.ex: I go back on the dole when the shooting season's finished.
example.tran: 狩猎季节过后，我又重靠领取救济金过活。

value.tran: 不复存在的;不再发生的

value.def: Someone or something that is finished is no longer important, powerful, or effective.

example.ex: Her power over me is finished...
He confessed: 'I thought I was finished.'
example.tran: 他承认道：“我以为自己已经完了。”

value.tran: 垮台的;完蛋的;失势的;失效的

value.def: Something that is finished or finished off in a particular way has been given a particular appearance or decoration.

example.ex: The dining room is finished in deep red...
Each dress is beautifully finished off with piped seams and fitted underskirts.
example.tran: 每件连衣裙最后线缝都滚了边，并且加上了合身的衬裙，看起来非常漂亮。

gramarinfo.label: v-link ADJ prep, oft adv ADJ

value.tran: (以某种方式的外观或装饰)最后呈现的

trans: 光制（精加工，已修整）表面
成品地板；面材所组构而成
